attributes.title: Ganesha Chaturthi Celebration  || 16 September 2007
attributes.description:
Name of the Event - Ganesha Chaturthi Celebration 
Venue- Duarte,  CA,  USA
Date - 16 September 2007 

In this video Supreme pontiff of Hinduism HDH #Nithyananadam Paramashivam offers worship to Sri Ananda Ganapathy at Duarte, CA on the occasion of Ganesh Chaturthi 

वक्र तुंड महाकाय, सूर्य कोटि समप्रभ:। निर्विघ्नं कुरु मे देव शुभ कार्येषु सर्वदा ॥ is a Prayer to Lord #Ganesha, to remove obstacles and bless with success. Lord Ganesha is prayed to at the beginning of all works as he is the deity who removes #obstacles. 
Darshan of our Sri  Ananda Ganapathy in Duarte, CA,  USA.
